nd Alternative Assets Credit Hours  3 EC 430   Financial Modeling Credit Hours  3 Plus one of the following Economics and Business Electives  BU 305   Intermediate Accounting Credit Hours  3 BU 415   Financial Statements Analysis Credit Hours  3 EC 307   International Finance Credit Hours  3 EC 405   Money and Banking Credit Hours  3   Back to Top   Print Degree Planner   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 